'''Mobail fuon''' a puotebl telifuon we kiah mek ah risiiv kaal uoba riedio friikuensi kiaria wails di yuuza a-muuv widin wah telifuon saabis ieria. Di riedio friikuensi lingk extablish kanekshan tu di suichin sistim tu wah mobail fuon aparieta, we provaid axes tu di poblik suich telifuon netwok (PSTN). Muos madan mobail telifuon saabis yuuz seliula netwok aachitecha, ah dierfuo mobail telifuon muotaim aalso kaal seliula telifuon ar sel fuon. Ina hadishan tu telifoni, 2000z-iira mobail fuon supuot wuoliip a adaels saabis, laka tex mechiz, MMS, iimiel, Intanet axes, shaat-rienj wayales komiunikieshan (infrared, Bluutut), biniz aplikieshan, giemin, ah dijital fotografi. Mobail fuon we haafa demaya ah muo jinaral kompyuutin kiepebiliti refa tu az smaatfuon.
